parameters.name: KeyPairName
parameters.description: The name of the key pair. The name must be 2 to 128 characters in length. The name must start with a letter and cannot start with `http://` or `https://`. The name can contain letters, digits, colons (:), underscores (\_), and hyphens (-).

parameters.name: RegionId
parameters.description: The ID of the region in which to create the key pair. You can call the [DescribeRegions](~~25609~~) operation to query the most recent region list.

parameters.name: ResourceGroupId
parameters.description: The ID of the resource group to which to add the key pair.

parameters.name: Tag
parameters.description: The tags of the key pair.
